{"tid":760643,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[公投] 樣衰/柒應唔應該玩coplay?","createTime":"2018-07-29T16:52:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-01T15:20:27.000Z","uid":16181,"like":62,"dislike":230,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"7481d6e5b9e3e976275321ee069b37e48d6ebe18","tid":760643,"uid":16181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T16:52:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/759684/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/759684/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/758114/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/758114/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n是咁的，動漫節一向都好多動漫迷鐘意玩角色扮演<br />\n有玩既，其實都會用好多心機，悉心打扮，去展覽場聚首一堂<br />\n大家本來應該報以掌聲、讚美去支持一班咁用心去發夢既人<br />\n<br />\n但係呢，連登就係香港人性既陰暗面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鐘意攻擊一班生得醜而又玩cosplay既香港人<br />\n但其實佢地都係做緊佢地自己鐘意既野<br />\n不過出黎既效果又的確幾不如意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n令我諗起西洋菜街俾人殺街，亦都係因為咁上下原因<br />\n<br />\n公投～<br />\n<ins>生得醜到底應唔應該玩Cosplay呢？</ins><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">支持年輕人玩下、發下夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n翻歸啦！咪撚再出黎獻世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"784eb719a61a5ab5d02f96081f4591c99095b9ae","tid":760643,"uid":16181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T16:53:31.000Z","msg":"標題係 [樣衰/柒應唔應該玩COSPLAY?]<br />\n<br />\n打漏左隻字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自膠"},{"pid":"5d97a3dba4d88fbb9557e4389e1a1ac8bfa86872","tid":760643,"uid":35667,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T16:53:57.000Z","msg":"但其實佢地都係做緊佢地自己鐘意既野<br />\n咪死返屋企慢慢玩囉"},{"pid":"da3c418c2ed51fe1c29019df7e74092bae914f8d","tid":760643,"uid":8307,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T16:54:24.000Z","msg":"要玩咪係屋企玩囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebfe692ceb0ce