aces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"723eb6f17ec76466e38a607168738aeb9b51c085","tid":760643,"uid":172844,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T17:13:01.000Z","msg":"其實我覺得樣唔係大問題<br />\n講真出cos都係對角色有愛姐<br />\n個問題會唔會係服飾化妝方面呢<br />\n我覺得出cos出到衫又錯  wig又錯<br />\n又或者突登賣肉  清純角色做姣pose<br />\n咁到底係出緊咩呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"747bc97c7d4d0390cd7212e614c50b7475fc787a","tid":760643,"uid":156771,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T17:18:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢個topic係連登有討論空間嫁咩<br />\n肥同柒就連呼吸都唔應該啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好話cosplay"},{"pid":"26198e1390a3231f3915ef6eb35c1c2d140c1f07","tid":760643,"uid":73143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T17:23:18.000Z","msg":"係連登開呢種post唔使睇都知邊面多人投<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ac0dd9eb2ee19b6a886ed5d6a74ac5ca436e725","tid":760643,"uid":44298,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T17:27:37.000Z","msg":"cos d唔洗出樣嘅未得囉"},{"pid":"aa154130b43de8a8ac22e50730d6a0711a7b79c3","tid":760643,"uid":16181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"747bc97c7d4d0390cd7212e614c50b7475fc787a","tid":760643,"uid":156771,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T17:18:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢個topic係連登有討論空間嫁咩<br />\n肥同柒就連呼吸都唔應該啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好話cosplay"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T17:34:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e411