eplyTime":"2018-07-29T22:35:24.000Z","msg":"我又覺得無咩所謂"},{"pid":"1efc9381d5f3bf793d92ed2069b621477a439229","tid":760643,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T00:13:57.000Z","msg":"應該立法將樣衰嘅人處死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffb5593af692a1fbb244f2a2556eec1c690af20d","tid":760643,"uid":35524,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T00:20:57.000Z","msg":"我自己覺得玩Cosplay真係無咩問題<br />\n天生樣衰都唔係問題<br />\n問題你如果認真對待你既興趣你你點都有方法執下自己 研究下化下妝<br />\n有好多無論件衫定其他配件武器都甩皮甩骨<br />\n戴假髮又露哂自己D頭髮出黎<br />\n身材都唔好話要跟足角色設定 但起馬唔好瘦既角色變左肥 極大隻既角色變左極瘦<br />\n樣樣都唔得個D我真係睇唔出有D咩愛係入面<br />\n就算你畢加索咁既樣 其他可以改變既野你係可以做 <br />\n唔好話咩天生樣衰應唔應該玩Cosplay <br />\n唔睇樣係其他角度都可以睇得出條友係咪真係認真對待自己"},{"pid":"9fa1994a8e5d465c758f616830754e7ab534de8a","tid":760643,"uid":8534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae9fdc91c49005ce10f51eee791c86a5d2b0e5d8","tid":760643,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6e4c542b400c26603f22d8490a9bb94718456acf","tid":760643,"uid":8534,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T16:57:01.000Z","msg":"樣就生定冇得改，不過佢哋都有盡力去化好個妝，都算係對角色同自己嘅一份尊重。不過好心肥嗰啲就咪參加啦，好意思㗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T22:15:32.000Z","msg":"咩叫生定冇得改?呢個世界有整容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T03:25:26.000Z","msg":"咁唔係個個都會走去整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7252300aefc853d2c659aae9af4c921812f45177","tid":760643,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fa1994a